### Changelog 0.14.1..79510cc

79510cc - Correct GitHub release user
e5ce8d4 - Remove stale build badge
3110d52 - Add automated plugin build and release via GitHub actions

**SHA256 Checksums**
```
300147ce8d2c1ca56986654083d60ab795489e2e9e3a11ea7a1f57566260fd14 *yaml-config-plugin-0.14.2-290.jar
```
* fix ability to set custom file pattern per configuration repository

* #47 adds support for referencing templates and specifying parameters
 * #32 adds better support for YAML aliases 
 * #46 introduces format_version field, with future work for v2 format 
 * #35 default file pattern is now `.gocd.yaml` or `.gocd.yml`

* added configrepo material type
 * added p4 material type support
